; Regression test for issue #2944: balance assignments must work with
; --permissive.  A balance-assignment-only posting (= $value with no
; explicit amount) should compute the posting amount from the target
; balance, even when --permissive is active.  The old bug left such
; postings with null amounts, causing "Only one posting with null amount"
; or "Cannot strip commodity annotations from an uninitialized amount".

2018/08/01 * First
    Assets:Foo             $12.34
    Equity:Opening Balances

2018/09/01 * Second
    Assets:Foo             $44.44
    Equity:Opening Balances

; Balance assignment: set Assets:Foo to $78.90 (adding $22.12)
2018/12/31 * Test Assignment
    Assets:Foo                                     = $78.90
    Equity:Opening Balances

test bal --permissive
              $78.90  Assets:Foo
             $-78.90  Equity:Opening Balances
--------------------
                   0
end test
